@*
    布局视图可以让WEB应用程序中所有的视图保持外观一致；看起来像ASP.NET WebForm中的母版页
    布局视图也具有.cshtml扩展名；ASP.NET Core中，布局页默认名称为_Layout.cshtml;其通常放在View/Shared文件夹里
    在一个应用程序中可以包含多个布局页视图
*@

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <environment include="Development">
        <link href="~/lib/twitter-bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet" />

    </environment>
    <environment exclude="Development">
        <link rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous"
              href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" asp-fallback-href="~/lib/twitter-bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css.map" 
              asp-fallback-test-class="sr-only" asp-fallback-test-property="position" asp-fallback-test-value="absolute">
 
        @*link里的integrity属性用于检查子资源完整性，Subresource Integrity(SRI)是一种安全功能，允许浏览器检查被检索的文件是否被恶意篡改*@
    </environment>

    <link href="~/css/site.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">

        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-danger navbar-dark">
            <a class="navbar-brand" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">
                <img src="~/images/image.png" width="30" height="30" />
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapsibleNavbar">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>

            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="collapsibleNavbar">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">列表</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Create">创建</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>

        @*添加Bootstrap的样式类container*@ @RenderBody()
    </div>

    @*布局页部分可选
    选项一： @RenderSection("自定义名称",required:false) required参数设置为False
    选项二：    @if (IsSectionDefined("自定义名称"))
    {
    @RenderSection("Scripts",required:false)
    }
    *@

    <script src="~/lib/jquery/jquery.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/twitter-bootstrap/js/bootstrap.js"></script>
    @if (IsSectionDefined("Scripts"))
    {
        @RenderSection("Scripts",required:false)
    }
</body>
</html>
